      "writtenOn": "2018-11-17T21:23:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Longer term, should this be an option to the swizzler (or skcms??), in that blitting should also take an (optional) Porter-Duff operator (i.e. Src vs SrcOverDst), so that transparent pixels in the src are either written to the dst or ignored?",
