      "message": "\u003e But the problem with that approach is that wuffs\u0027 output is a paletted image (though maybe there\u0027s an option to change that?).\n\nWuffs today doesn\u0027t have that option, but I\u0027ve been meaning to add that option at some point. I could reprioritize to \u0027soon\u0027 if that\u0027ll help.",
